    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='222:249'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-1a' );" name="024-1a" class="pb">[024-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='249:263'>禮記要義卷第二十五　祭統</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='263:279'>　一祭非自外至心怵而奉之以禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='279:299'>夫祭者非物自外至者也自中出生於心也心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='299:319'>怵而奉之以禮是故唯賢者能盡祭之義注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='319:339'>怵感念親之貌也正義曰自猶從也言孝子祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='339:359'>親非假他物從外至於身使巳爲之但從孝子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='359:371'>身中出生於孝子之心也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='371:387'>　二請玉女共事宗社此求助之本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='387:407'>國君取夫人之辭曰請君之玉女與寡人共有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='407:434'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-1b' );" name="024-1b" class="pb">[024-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='434:454'>敝邑事宗廟社稷此求助之本也注云言玉女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='454:468'>者美言之也君子於玉比德焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='468:481'>　三盡物盡志身致其誠信</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='481:501'>水草之菹陸産之醢小物備矣三牲之爼八簋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='501:521'>之實美物備矣昆蟲之異草木之實隂陽之物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='521:541'>備矣凢天之所生地之所長茍可薦者莫不咸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='541:561'>在示盡物也外則盡物内則盡志此祭之心也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='561:581'>是故天子親耕於南郊以共齊盛王后蠶於北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='581:601'>郊以共純服諸侯耕於東郊亦以共齊盛夫人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='601:628'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-2a' );" name="024-2a" class="pb">[024-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='628:648'>蠶於北郊以共冕服天子諸侯非莫耕也王后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='648:668'>夫人非莫蠶也身致其誠信誠信之謂盡盡之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='668:688'>謂敬敬盡然後可以事神明此祭之道也注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='688:708'>水草之菹芹苑之屬陸産之醢蚳蝝之屬天子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='708:728'>之祭八簋昆蟲謂温生寒死之蟲也内則可食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='728:748'>之物有蜩范草木之實蓤芡榛栗之屬咸皆也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='748:768'>純服亦冕服也玄言之爾純以見繒色冕以著</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='768:788'>祭服東郊少陽諸侯象也夫人不蠶於西郊婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='788:799'>人禮少變也齊或作粢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='799:826'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-2b' );" name="024-2b" class="pb">[024-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='826:842'>　四鄭讀純有二義文與音亦不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='842:862'>正義曰純服亦冕服也者天子云純諸侯言冕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='862:882'>冕祭服故知純亦是祭服天子言衣色諸侯亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='882:902'>有衣色是其互也鄭氏之意凢言純者其義有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='902:922'>二一絲旁才是古之緇字二是絲旁屯是純字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='922:942'>但書文相亂雖是緇字並皆作純鄭氏所注於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='942:962'>絲理可知於色不明者即讀爲緇即論語云今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='962:982'>也純儉及此純服皆讀爲黒色若衣色見絲文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='982:993'>不明者讀純以爲絲也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='993:1020'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-3a' );" name="024-3a" class="pb">[024-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1020:1035'>　五君夫人散致齊及祼薦之節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1035:1055'>君致齊於外夫人致齊於内者外謂君之路寢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1055:1075'>内謂夫人正寢是致齊並皆於正寢其實散齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1075:1095'>亦然但此文對㑹於大廟故云君致齊於外夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1095:1115'>人致齊於内耳　然後㑹於大廟者祭曰君與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1115:1135'>夫人俱至大廟之中廟即始祖廟也夫人副禕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1135:1155'>立於東房者副及禕后之上服魯及二王之後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1155:1175'>夫人得服之侯伯夫人揄狄子男夫人闕狄而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1175:1195'>並立東房以俟行事尸旣入之後轉就西房故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1195:1222'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-3b' );" name="024-3b" class="pb">[024-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1222:1242'>禮器云夫人在房雖不云東西房下云夫人東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1242:1261'>酌罍尊則知夫人在房謂西房也大宗執璋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1261:1281'>瓉亞祼者大宗主宗廟禮者以亞祼之禮夫人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1281:1301'>親爲之此不云夫人而云大宗者記有廣言容</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1301:1321'>夫人有故故大宗伯代夫人行禮執璋瓉亞祼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1321:1341'>之禮圭瓉璋瓉並是祼器也以圭璋爲柄酌鬱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1341:1361'>鬯曰祼也宗婦執盎齊從夫人而來奠盎齊於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1361:1381'>位夫人乃就盎齊之尊酌此涗齊而薦之者因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1381:1401'>盎齊有明水連言水耳夫人薦豆者於君羞嚌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1401:1428'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-4a' );" name="024-4a" class="pb">[024-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1428:1440'>之時夫人薦此饋食之豆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1440:1453'>　六重祼重升歌重武宿夜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1453:1473'>夫祭有三重焉獻之屬莫重於祼聲莫重於升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1473:1493'>歌舞莫重於武宿夜此周道也凡三道者所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1493:1513'>假於外而以増君子之志也故與志進退志輕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1513:1533'>則亦輕志重則亦重注云武宿夜武曲名也周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1533:1553'>道猶周之禮正義曰舞莫重於武宿夜者武宿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1553:1573'>夜是武曲之名是衆舞之中無能重於武宿夜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1573:1593'>之舞皇氏曰師說書傳云武王伐紂至於商郊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1593:1620'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-4b' );" name="024-4b" class="pb">[024-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1620:1640'>停止宿夜士卒皆歡樂歌舞以待旦因名焉武</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1640:1658'>宿夜其樂亡也熊氏云此即大武之樂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1658:1669'>　七尸亦餕鬼神之餘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1669:1689'>是故古之君子曰尸亦餕鬼神之餘也者又引</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1689:1709'>古言證餕義也言亦者亦人餕尸之餘乃是人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1709:1730'>食尸餘而云尸亦餕鬼神餘者若王侯𥘉薦毛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1730:1750'>血燔燎是薦於鬼神至薦孰時尸乃食之是尸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1750:1770'>餕鬼神之餘若大夫士隂厭亦是先薦鬼神而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1770:1782'>後尸乃食亦尸餕鬼神餘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1782:1809'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-5a' );" name="024-5a" class="pb">[024-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1809:1820'>八二簋留陽厭四簋餕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1820:1840'>是故以四簋黍見其脩於廟中也者謂餕之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1840:1860'>君與三卿以四簋之黍脩整普徧也所以用四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1860:1880'>簋多黍而餕者欲見其恩惠脩整徧於廟中諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1880:1900'>侯之祭有六簋今云以四簋者以二簋留爲陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1900:1920'>厭之祭故以四簋而餕簋有黍稷特云黍者見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1920:1930'>其美舉黍稷可知也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1930:1943'>　九君子事君恕已乃行之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1943:1963'>是故君子之事君也必身行之所不安於上則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1963:1990'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-5b' );" name="024-5b" class="pb">[024-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1990:2010'>不以使下所惡於下則不以事上非諸人行諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2010:2030'>已非教之道也注云必身行之言恕已乃行之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2030:2044'>　十設同几詔祝於室出于祊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2044:2064'>鋪筵設同几爲依神也詔祝於室而出于祊此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2064:2084'>交神明之道也注云同之言詷也祭者以其妃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2084:2104'>配亦不特几也詔祝告事於尸也岀於祊謂索</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2104:2125'>祭也正義曰設之曰筵坐之曰席同之言詷詷共</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2125:2145'>也言人生時形體異故夫婦別几死則䰟氣同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2145:2165'>歸於此故夫婦共几鋪席設几使神依之設此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2165:2192'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-6a' );" name="024-6a" class="pb">[024-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2192:2212'>夫婦所共之几席亦共之必云同几者筵席旣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2212:2232'>長几則短小恐其各設故特云同几　詔祝於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2232:2252'>室者詔告也祝祝也謂祝官以言詔告祝請其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2252:2272'>尸於室求之　而岀于祊者謂明日繹祭而出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2272:2292'>廟門旁廣求神於門外之祊古文字林皆訓詷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2292:2312'>爲共是漢魏之時字義如此是以讀同爲詷今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2312:2332'>則揔爲一字云祭者以其妃配者儀禮少牢文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2332:2352'>謂祭夫祝辭云以某妃配云亦不特几也者謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2352:2372'>不但不特設辭亦不特設其几謂祝辭與几皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2372:2399'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-6b' );" name="024-6b" class="pb">[024-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2399:2419'>同於夫不特設也故鄭注司几筵云祭於廟同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2419:2426'>几精氣合也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2426:2448'><span class='krp-note'>十/一</span>尸用同姓適孫父北靣事之一云西靣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2448:2468'>夫祭之道孫爲王父尸所使爲尸者於祭者子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2468:2488'>行也父北靣而事之所以明子事父之道也此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2488:2508'>父子之倫也注云子行猶子列也祭祖則用孫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2508:2528'>列皆取於同姓之適孫也天子諸侯之祭朝事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2528:2548'>延尸於户外是以有北靣事尸之禮正義曰以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2548:2568'>少牢特牲尸皆在室之奥主人西靣事之無北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2568:2595'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-7a' );" name="024-7a" class="pb">[024-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2595:2610'>靣事尸之禮故知是天子諸侯也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2610:2623'><span class='krp-note'>十/二</span>酳尸獻賔之節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2623:2643'>尸飲五君洗玉爵獻卿尸飲七以瑶爵獻大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2643:2663'>尸飲九以散爵獻士及羣有司皆以齒明尊卑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2663:2683'>之等也注云尸飲五謂酳尸五獻也大夫士祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2683:2703'>三獻而獻賔正義曰此據備九獻之禮者至主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2703:2723'>人酳尸故尸飲五也凡祭二獻祼用鬱鬯尸祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2723:2743'>奠而不飲朝踐二獻饋食二獻及食畢主人酳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2743:2763'>尸此等皆尸飲之故云尸飲五於此之時以獻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2763:2790'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-7b' );" name="024-7b" class="pb">[024-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2790:2810'>卿獻卿之後乃主婦酳尸酳尸畢賔長獻尸是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2810:2831'>尸飲七也乃瑶爵獻大夫是正九獻禮畢但𥘉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2831:2851'>二祼不飲故云尸飲七自此以後長賔長兄弟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2851:2871'>更爲加爵尸又飲二是并前尸飲九主人乃散</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2871:2891'>爵獻士及羣有司也此謂上公九獻故以酳尸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2891:2911'>之一獻爲尸飲五也若侯伯七獻朝踐饋食時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2911:2931'>各一獻食訖酳尸但尸飲三也子男五獻食訖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2931:2951'>酳尸尸飲一云大夫士祭三獻而獻賔者欲明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2951:2971'>諸侯獻賔時節與大夫士獻賔不同知大夫士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2971:2998'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-8a' );" name="024-8a" class="pb">[024-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2998:3018'>祭三獻而獻賔者特牲禮文下大夫不賔尸與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3018:3038'>士同亦三獻而獻賔知者有司徹文其上大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3038:3049'>別行賔尸之禮此異也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3049:3067'><span class='krp-note'>十/三</span>尸主有昭穆主賔亦爲昭穆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3067:3087'>有事於大廟則羣昭羣穆咸在而不失其倫此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3087:3107'>之謂親䟽之殺也注云昭穆咸在同宗父子皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3107:3127'>來正義曰父南靣子北靣親者近䟽者逺又各</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3127:3147'>有次序是故有事於大廟則羣昭羣穆咸在者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3147:3167'>祭大廟之時則衆廟尸主皆來及助祭之人同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3167:3194'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-8b' );" name="024-8b" class="pb">[024-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3194:3214'>宗父子皆至則羣昭穆咸在若不於大廟餘廟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3214:3234'>之祭唯有當廟尸主及所出之廟子孫來至不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3234:3254'>得羣昭羣穆咸在也　而不失其倫者尸主旣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3254:3274'>有昭穆故主人及衆賔亦爲昭穆列在廟不失</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3274:3278'>倫類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3278:3297'><span class='krp-note'>十/四</span>賜爵禄於太廟所命者北靣受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3297:3317'>古者明君爵有德而禄有功必賜爵禄於大廟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3317:3337'>示不敢專也故祭之日一獻君降立于阼階之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3337:3357'>南南郷所命北靣史由君右執䇿命之再拜稽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3357:3384'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-9a' );" name="024-9a" class="pb">[024-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3384:3404'>首受書以歸而舎奠于其廟此爵賞之施也注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3404:3424'>云一奠一酳尸也舎當爲釋聲之誤也非時而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3424:3445'>祭曰奠正義曰經云一獻知非𥘉祼及朝踐饋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3445:3465'>食之一獻必爲一酳尸者以一酳尸之前皆爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3465:3485'>祭事承奉鬼神未暇䇿命而尸食巳畢祭事方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3485:3505'>了始可以行其爵賞及賜勞臣下此一獻則上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3505:3525'>尸飲五君獻卿之時也若天子命羣臣則不因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3525:3545'>常祭之日特假於廟故大宗伯云王命諸侯則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3545:3564'>儐注云王將岀命假祖廟立依前南郷是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3564:3591'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-9b' );" name="024-9b" class="pb">[024-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3591:3608'><span class='krp-note'>十/五</span>夫婦授受不襲處不承爵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3608:3628'>夫人薦豆執校者校謂豆之中央直者夫人薦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3628:3648'>豆之時手執此校執醴授之執鐙者鐙謂豆下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3648:3668'>跗夫人薦豆之時此執醴之人以豆授夫人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3668:3688'>時則執豆之下跗夫人授之乃執校也尸酢夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3688:3708'>人執柄者爵爲雀形以尾爲柄夫人獻尸尸酢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3708:3728'>夫人尸則執雀尾授夫人也夫人爲尸執足者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3728:3748'>夫人授酢於尸則執爵足也夫婦相授受不相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3748:3768'>襲處者謂夫婦交相致爵之時襲因也其執之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3768:3796'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-10a' );" name="024-10a" class="pb">[024-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3796:3816'>物不相因故處若夫婦交相致爵不得執故處</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3816:3836'>以明男女有別　酢必易爵者謂夫婦交相致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3836:3856'>爵之時主人受主婦之酢易換其爵故特牲主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3856:3876'>人受主婦之酢爵更爵酢鄭注云主人更爵自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3876:3886'>酢男子不承婦人爵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3886:3902'><span class='krp-note'>十/六</span>俎以骨爲主前貴於後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3902:3922'>凡爲俎者以骨爲主骨有貴賤殷人貴髀周人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3922:3942'>貴肩凡前貴於後俎者所以明祭之必有惠也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3942:3962'>注云殷人貴髀爲其厚也周人貴肩爲其顯也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3962:3990'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-10b' );" name="024-10b" class="pb">[024-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3990:4004'>凡前貴於後謂脊脅臂臑之屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4004:4023'><span class='krp-note'>十/七</span>旅酬時賜助祭者爵昭穆各齒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4023:4043'>凡賜爵昭爲一穆爲一昭與昭齒穆與穆齒凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4043:4063'>羣有司皆以齒此之謂長㓜有序注云昭穆猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4063:4083'>特牲少牢饋食之禮衆兄弟也羣有司猶衆賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4083:4103'>下及執事者君賜之爵謂若酬之正義曰謂祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4103:4123'>祀旅酬時賜助祭者酒爵故云賜爵特牲饋食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4123:4144'>禮𥘉有主人獻衆賔兄弟之禮後乃旅酬衆賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4144:4164'>兄弟此經直云賜爵知非獻時而特云酬者以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4164:4192'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-11a' );" name="024-11a" class="pb">[024-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4192:4212'>獻時不以昭穆爲次者此云昭與昭齒穆與穆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4212:4226'>齒當旅酬之事故知賜爵爲酬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4226:4244'><span class='krp-note'>十/八</span>卑煇胞翟閽至尊不忘至賤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4244:4264'>祭有卑煇胞翟閽者惠下之道也煇者甲吏之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4264:4284'>賤者也胞者肉吏之賤者也翟者樂吏之賤者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4284:4303'>也閽者守門之賤者也古者不使刑人守門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4303:4323'>此四守者吏之至賤者也尸又至尊以至尊旣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4323:4343'>祭之末而不忘至賤而以其餘卑之注云煇周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4343:4363'>禮作韗謂韗磔皮革之官也翟謂教羽舞者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4363:4391'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-11b' );" name="024-11b" class="pb">[024-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4391:4411'>古者不使刑人守門謂夏殷時正義曰古者不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4411:4431'>使刑人守門者此作記之人以見周刑人守門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4431:4451'>以祭末又得恩賜與刑人故明之云古者夏殷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4451:4470'>之時不使刑人守門雖是賤人所以得恩賜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4470:4487'><span class='krp-note'>十/九</span>禘發爵賜服嘗出田邑等</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4487:4507'>古者於禘也發爵賜服順陽義也於嘗也出田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4507:4527'>邑發秋政順隂義也故記曰甞之日發公室示</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4527:4547'>賞也草艾則墨未發秋政則民弗敢草也注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4547:4567'>言爵命屬陽國地屬隂發公室出賞物也草艾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4567:4595'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-12a' );" name="024-12a" class="pb">[024-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4595:4615'>謂艾取草也秋草木成可芟艾給爨亨時則始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4615:4621'>行小刑也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4621:4638'><span class='krp-note'>二/十</span>義章雖不親祭於義不失</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4638:4658'>夫義者所以濟志也諸德之發也是故其德盛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4658:4678'>者其志厚其志厚者其義章其義章者其祭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4678:4698'>敬祭敬則竟内之子孫莫敢不敬矣是故君子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4698:4718'>之祭也必身親涖之有故則使人可也雖使人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4718:4738'>也君不失其義者君明其義故也注云濟成也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4738:4758'>發謂機發也竟内之子孫萬人爲子孫涖臨也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4758:4786'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-12b' );" name="024-12b" class="pb">[024-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4786:4806'>君不失其義者言君雖不自親祭祭禮無闕於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4806:4813'>君德不損也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4813:4832'><span class='krp-note'>卄/乙</span>秋賜侯氏車服等四時皆有賞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4832:4852'>正義曰案左傳云賞以春夏刑以秋冬此嘗之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4852:4872'>日發公室示賞者文各有所對以賞對刑則賞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4872:4892'>屬春夏刑屬秋冬其實四時之間皆有賞故車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4892:4912'>服屬夏田邑屬秋岀田邑之時亦有物也故覲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4912:4926'>禮秋時賜侯氏車服及篋服也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4926:4943'><span class='krp-note'>卄/二</span>觀銘旣美所稱又美所爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4943:4971'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-13a' );" name="024-13a" class="pb">[024-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4971:4991'>君子之觀於銘也旣美其所稱又美其所爲爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4991:5011'>之者明足以見之仁足以與之知足以利之可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5011:5031'>謂賢矣賢而勿伐可謂恭矣注云美其所爲美</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5031:5051'>此人爲此銘明足以見之見其先祖之美也仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5051:5071'>足以與之與其先祖之銘也非有仁恩君不使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5071:5091'>與之也知足以利之利己名得比於先祖正義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5091:5111'>曰所稱謂先祖也所爲謂巳身行業也君子有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5111:5131'>德之士觀銘必見此二事之美爲之者謂爲銘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5131:5136'>之人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5136:5164'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-13b' );" name="024-13b" class="pb">[024-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5164:5183'><span class='krp-note'>卄/三</span>衛莊公䇿命孔悝稱其祖之美</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5183:5203'>公曰叔舅乃祖莊叔左右成公成公乃命莊叔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5203:5223'>隨難于漢陽即宫于宗周奔走無射注曰叔舅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5223:5243'>者公爲䇿書尊呼孔悝而命之也乃猶女也莊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5243:5263'>叔悝七丗之祖衛大夫孔逹也隨難者謂成公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5263:5283'>爲晉文公所伐出奔楚命莊叔從焉漢楚之川</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5283:5303'>也即宫於宗周後反得國坐殺弟叔武晉人執</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5303:5323'>而歸之於京師寘之深室也射厭也言莊叔常</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5323:5343'>奔走至勞苦而不厭倦也周旣去鎬京猶名王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5343:5371'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-14a' );" name="024-14a" class="pb">[024-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5371:5378'>城爲宗周也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5378:5396'><span class='krp-note'>卄/五</span>孔悝對揚君命施于烝彞鼎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5396:5416'>悝拜稽首曰對揚以辟之勤大命施于烝彞鼎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5416:5436'>此衛孔悝之鼎銘也注云對遂也辟明也言遂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5436:5456'>揚君命以明我先祖之德也施猶著也言我將</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5456:5476'>行君之命又刻著於烝祭之彞鼎彞尊也周禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5476:5496'>大約劑書於宗彞言銘之類衆多也略取此一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5496:5501'>以言之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5501:5519'><span class='krp-note'>卄/六</span>蒯聵孔悝雖無令德於禮是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5519:5547'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-14b' );" name="024-14b" class="pb">[024-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5547:5567'>古之君子論譔其先祖之美而明著之後丗者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5567:5587'>也以比其身以重其國家如此注云如莊公命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5587:5607'>孔悝之爲也莊公孔悝雖無令德以終其事於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5607:5614'>禮是行之非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5614:5630'><span class='krp-note'>卄/七</span>康周公故賜魯以重祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5630:5650'>昔者周公旦有勲勞於天下周公旣没成王康</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5650:5670'>王追念周公之所以勲勞者而欲尊魯故賜之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5670:5690'>以重祭外祭則郊社是也内祭則大嘗禘是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5690:5710'>夫大嘗禘升歌清廟下而管象朱干玉戚以舞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5710:5738'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-15a' );" name="024-15a" class="pb">[024-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5738:5758'>大武八佾以舞大夏此天子之樂也康周公故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5758:5778'>以賜魯也注云言此者王室所銘若周公之功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5778:5798'>清廟頌文王之詩也管象吹管而舞武象之樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5798:5818'>也朱干赤盾戚斧也此武象之舞所執也佾猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5818:5838'>列也大夏禹樂文舞也執羽籥文武之舞皆八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5838:5858'>列互言之耳康猶褒大也易晉卦曰康侯用錫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5858:5861'>馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5861:5872'>禮記要義卷第二十五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5872:5900'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '024-15b' );" name="024-15b" class="pb">[024-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
